description:
Modern matchmaking: more friends, more fun, more love. Play Woo to matchmake your friends or, if you’re single, get a little help in the game of love.


Matchmakers
––––––––––––

- Play Woo to matchmake your single friends. See profiles and check yes or no to send them on to your friends. 
- Put your matchmaking prowess to the test—find out if you pick profiles that become romantic matches.  
- Chat about your selections, and find out when your suggestions result in a match.
- Stay in sync with your friends as they date.
- Help multiple single friends find love.


Daters
––––––

- Play Woo to check out available singles near you.
- Only see people who have matched with you. 
- Invite friends to help you find love. They’ll pick your potential dates, suggest profile changes, and chat with you.
- Invite as many friends as you’d like to help you find the best matches. 
- Share profiles and date stories with your friends. 


Key Features
–––––––––––

- Friend-approved matches
- In-app messaging group chat
- Unique profile filtering by friends
- Profile pages show pics, friend-written testimonials, and mutual friends
